Package codigo.ProyectoAlgoritmos

Class Nodo

java.lang.Object
codigo.ProyectoAlgoritmos.Nodo
public class Nodo extends Object
Class that represents a node in a linked data structure. Each node contains information about a procedure, including your name, method content, complexity, and counters various operations within the method.
